verbose_text: Treatment of Nlrp3 -/- and Asc -/- iBMDMs with ATP (XREF_FIG A) or nigericin (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY F) did not deplete UBE2L3; similarly treated Casp1/4 -/- and Casp1 -/- iBMDMs retained UBE2L3 protein (XREF_FIG A, XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY F, and S1G).
